BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:n1eyzWgp70Xby58qU5fuP
SUMMARY:Zumba Toning *Online*
DTSTAMP:20260314T153110Z
DTSTART:20260318T081500Z
DESCRIPTION:Tailored for active older adults\\\, who want to focus on muscl
	e conditioning and light weight activity\\\, Zumba Gold Toning blends low-
	intensity strength training with a fun party atmosphere. Dress comfortably
	 and bring water. Adults of all ages welcome. Start anytime. Please contac
	t arielb@phinneycenter.org for link to attend this online-only class.\n\nh
	ttps://www.phinneycenter.org/event/zumba-toning-gold-online/2026-03-18/\n\
	nFrom Phinney Neighborhood Association (PNA)
URL:https://www.phinneycenter.org/event/zumba-toning-gold-online/2026-03-18
